        {
            "title": "對沖基金集體大豐收 去年全行業創下16年來最佳回報率",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg reporting\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"4453\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/D2NCcM6PBsYVdEEcC1hSMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0NTM7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a49911c3d2001fbab8d6c08569dd6399\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg reporting</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 自從全球金融危機以後，對沖基金投資者已經很久沒有像現在這麼「好過」了。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據行業追蹤機構Hedge Fund Research Inc.匯編的數據，這個規模約5萬億美元的行業去年取得了約12.6%的回報，表現為2009年以來最佳。人工智能熱潮、地緣政治衝擊以及利率前景的不確定性令市場大幅波動，而這正好為那些以波動性為生的交易策略創造了諸多機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由D.E. Shaw、Millennium Management、城堡、Point72 Asset Management和Qube Research &amp; Technologies等行業巨頭管理的基金紛紛錄得兩位數回報。橋水基金旗艦產品Pure Alpha II更是創下34%的歷史最高回報率。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-39fe6424-d21e-34e6-bbb7-5a6d3ac001ec-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"視頻：對沖基金在2025年迎來輝煌的一年。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/d6Z7K.lKwMBDtpU9FetrZg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/713252079839b826bb89b10fba5d69ea\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">視頻：對沖基金在2025年迎來輝煌的一年。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通常來說，專注單一策略的小型基金憑借靈活的倉位調整往往能在個別年份跑贏大盤，即便整個行業表現低迷，這類基金也斬獲頗豐。但即便是那些在多種策略中配置了數十億美元、以分散化換取穩定回報的大型機構，2025年大多也再次實現了兩位數回報。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「2025年是所有人都賺錢的一年，」對沖基金ADAPT Investment Managers首席投資官Alexis Maubourguet表示，「這種情況相當罕見。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在宏觀交易員受益於高波動環境的同時，股票型對沖基金也搭上了由人工智能推動的股市順風車。標普500指數去年上漲18%。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"4453\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DH.A94.djfpmRSi7rVzOsA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQ0NTM7Y2Y9d2VicA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/97892f1ed8794bef0ef9e4ca5d450fe3\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Hedge Funds Turn Chaos Into Cash for Best Gains in 16 Years (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Hema Parmar.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E9%9B%86%E9%AB%94%E5%A4%A7%E8%B1%90%E6%94%B6-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E8%A1%8C%E6%A5%AD%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B16%E5%B9%B4%E4%BE%86%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E5%9B%9E%E5%A0%B1%E7%8E%87-185023316.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-14 03:26:02",
